<Resource name="jdbc/Database_Name"
      global="jdbc/Database_Name"
      auth="Container"
      type="javax.sql.DataSource"
      driverClassName="com.mysql.jdbc.Driver"
      url="jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/Database_Name"
      username="User_Name"
      password="password"
       
      maxActive="100"
      maxIdle="20"
      minIdle="5"
      maxWait="10000"/>


1. copy and paste above code in context.xml file of apache tomcat. 
2. change "Database_Name", "User_Name" and "password" field.
3. Go to hibernate.cfg.xml file (PayRollSys/src/java/hibernate.cfg.xml) and Change the "Database_Name" in "hibernate.connection.datasource" 	  property.
4. Congratulation ! You are all done.

